 *
 * Test fixture for issue #3937: a ModelDesign of object instances whose
 * TypeDefinition references an ObjectType defined in a separate NodeSet2
 * file (Priklad02-EquipmentTypes.xml). Derived from the models attached
 * to the issue by @STUBA-rupr.
